1、患者女性，50岁。2、既往体健&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;。3、患者缘于5天前无明显诱因出现发热，体温最高达39.5℃，继而3天前出现咳痰，咳少许白痰，无咳血及喘憋，自行应用药物（具体不详）后症状无减轻，2天前病情较前加重，伴痰中带血，仍有发热寒战，无胸痛、喘憋，无胸闷、气短、心慌，无恶心呕吐，无反酸烧心，无腹痛腹泻；今日为进一步诊治来我院就诊，行胸部DR示右上肺炎，遂以&ldquo;肺炎&rdquo;收治入院。&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;4.查体：&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;T 36.7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;℃&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;P70次&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;分&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;R18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;次&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;分&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;BP 120/70mmHg&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;，神清、精神可，咽部充血，扁桃体无肿大，口唇无发绀，未见颈静脉怒张及颈动脉异常搏动。胸廓对称，双肺呼吸音粗，右上肺可闻及散在细小湿啰音，无哮鸣音，左肺未闻及干湿性啰音，心界不大，心率70&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;分，律齐，未闻及早搏，各瓣膜听诊区未闻及病理性杂音。腹软，全腹无压痛、反跳痛及肌紧张，肝脾肋下未触及，肠鸣音正常存在。双下肢无水肿。&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#333333&quot;&gt;双侧肱二三头肌腱及跟膝腱反射正常存在，双侧&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Babinski&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;征及克氏症均阴性。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style='font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;'&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;5.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;辅助检查：2016-12-15双滦区医院行胸部DR：右上肺炎&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;